page.title: 10The Warren
page.content: The Warren has got {fifty acres.} Before Mr and Mrs Browning came it used to be a stable and they used to live in the big white house next door to them. They sold the house but still own all the land.The servants and stable boys used to live up above the stables.They rent all their land to a farmer who lives nearby.The Warren was {built in 1850.}They haven't got a well but on the map it says they have.The have got a mixture of coniferous and deciduous trees.They haven't got chickens.They have got two Shetland Ponies and a tame male pheasant who can feed out of your hand and sometimes he brings his mate.They let people they know come and look around their very big garden.
